commit.message:
config.shared (depend.new): delete libc-lock.h from dependencies, and fix _G_config.h -> $(_G_CONFIG_H) rule

	* config.shared (depend.new): delete libc-lock.h from
	dependencies, and fix _G_config.h -> $(_G_CONFIG_H) rule
	* depend: Rebuilt.

From-SVN: r23008

+

+	* depend: Rebuilt.
+
